    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虚张声势并加大赌注，提高您的扑克技巧，不断积攒经验，结交新朋友，直至成为史上最棒的玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/b66fc1476bbee373e01652b2b236f74f.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/b66fc1476bbee373e01652b2b236f74f.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/b66fc1476bbee373e01652b2b236f74f.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 游戏特色 ◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>免费筹码</strong> - 每天登录游戏即可获得免费筹码！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BOOST POKER 锦标赛</strong> - 是一种德州扑克锦标赛，旋转轮轴就有机会赢取 150 亿筹码！用这款令人激动的游戏来增加您的余额！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特殊模式</strong> - 玩带有变化的德州扑克：用王牌组成超级组合、偷看对手的牌、只玩大牌、获得扑克对子等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MTT 锦标赛</strong> - 最流行的线下锦标赛现在可以在线玩啦！在多个牌桌击败众多名不虚传的竞争对手即可杀入决赛桌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锦标赛</strong> – 参加每周 Sit'n'Go 锦标赛，可赢取独特奖杯或成千上万的筹码，并在排行榜上取得名次晋升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>棋牌室游戏</strong> - 畅玩各种各样的棋牌室游戏。玩二十一点、奥马哈扑克、轮盘、百家乐、老虎机、电动扑克、双骰子、Split Bet Poker 和 Set Poker，所有游戏尽在一个应用！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VIP 等级</strong> - 获得丰厚奖励和访问游戏内最新功能的专属权限！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>确保游戏公平</strong> - 我们的所有游戏都使用随机数生成器 (RNG) 并经由独立专家认证。我们保证提供最棒、最公平的德州扑克游戏体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与其他玩家聊天</strong> - 通过我们方便的游戏内聊天、即时通讯工具和动画表情符号，在棋牌室牌桌上享受更多乐趣。与您的扑克对手和好友讨论已玩的手牌或分享您的表情符号！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>推荐系统</strong> - 邀请好友来玩，你们都将得到奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建立您的个人资料</strong> - 与好友分享您的成功。展示您玩过多少种游戏、您的重大胜利、等级、纸牌收藏、成就、道具和奖杯！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的头像</strong> - 在头像编辑器中创建独一无二的外表。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>任务</strong> - 完成每日任务可获取免费筹码！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法简单易学</strong> - 您是德州扑克新手，但一直想尝试玩一下？我们简单易学的教材模式将帮助您迈出第一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无需注册</strong> - 直接开玩。无需注册，即可通过访客模式使用我们的免费棋牌应用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单一账户</strong> -可在不同的设备上游玩。选择最适合您的授权方法，并立即开始免费玩德州扑克！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想体验除扑克外的其他游戏？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩我们的其他游戏，感受难忘的 3D 体验：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/1319c78bb50ea4b59a83eaa5f5013033.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/1319c78bb50ea4b59a83eaa5f5013033.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/1319c78bb50ea4b59a83eaa5f5013033.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轮盘</strong> – 具有惊艳的 3D 图形和三种轮盘桌：法式、美式和欧式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/ef032eef27b17171f76164376b1546d3.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/ef032eef27b17171f76164376b1546d3.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/ef032eef27b17171f76164376b1546d3.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>二十一点</strong> – 简单的“21 点”游戏。任何一个二十一点粉丝玩家都肯定会喜欢的激动人心的 3D 游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/6163349d4cb959631248b1df2edeb151.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/6163349d4cb959631248b1df2edeb151.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/6163349d4cb959631248b1df2edeb151.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>老虎机</strong> – 探索我们主题老虎机上的众多独特功能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/5f70cf297cb6c008f4cbc100c7c03796.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/5f70cf297cb6c008f4cbc100c7c03796.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/5f70cf297cb6c008f4cbc100c7c03796.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奥马哈扑克</strong> – 一种更动态的扑克游戏，手中有 4 张牌。 更多惊人组合让您体验更多乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/a80e378ffbe55cc6ef14b1deba06c917.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/a80e378ffbe55cc6ef14b1deba06c917.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/a80e378ffbe55cc6ef14b1deba06c917.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双骰子</strong> – 有史以来第一款 3D 双骰子游戏。下注、掷骰子、勇于冒险，成为最棒的双骰子玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/d9866578c5808494a81546d650794fbb.poster.avif?t=1771241255\" width=1170 height=568 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/d9866578c5808494a81546d650794fbb.webm?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174070/extras/d9866578c5808494a81546d650794fbb.mp4?t=1771241255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏仅对达法定年龄的玩家开放。游戏并不提供任何金钱或其他价值物奖励。在游戏中取得成功，并不表示您在真正的赌场游戏中也能取得成功。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >华盛顿州玩家通知</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于华盛顿州法律限制，我们暂不向该地区的玩家开放此游戏。为此给您带来的不便，我们深表歉意，并感谢您的理解。</p>",
